n    \"source_url\": \"https://minimalistbaker.com/easy-whole-wheat-banana-bread/\",\n    \"thumbnail_image_url\": \"https://minimalistbaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/EASY-Whole-Wheat-Banana-Bread-1-bowl-underect-oil-sugar-fluffy-delicious-minimalistbaker-6.jpg\",\n    \"ingredients\": [\n      \"3 medium ripe bananas (mashed)\",\n      \"1/3 cup melted coconut oil (or avocado oil)\",\n      \"1/2 cup coconut sugar (or brown sugar)\",\n      \"1/4 cup maple syrup (or honey)\",\n      \"2 large eggs (or flax eggs for a vegan option)\",\n      \"1 tsp baking soda\",\n      \"1/2 tsp sea salt\",\n      \"1 tsp ground cinnamon\",\n      \"1 tsp vanilla extract\",\n      \"1 3/4 cups whole wheat pastry flour (or white whole wheat)\",\n      \"1/2 cup chopped walnuts or chocolate chips (optional)\"\n    ],\n    \"cooking_instructions_summary\": \"Preheat your oven to 325°F (162°C) and grease a 9x5-inch loaf pan. In a large bowl, beat the mashed bananas and oil together. Whisk in the sugar, maple syrup, eggs, baking soda, salt, cinnamon, and vanilla extract. Gently stir in the whole wheat flour until just incorporated (do not overmix). Fold in walnuts or chocolate chips if using. Pour into the pan and bake for 55 to 65 minutes. Let cool in the pan for 10 minutes before transferring to a wire rack.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"recipe_title\": \"1-Bowl Chocolate Chip Banana Bread (Vegan + GF)\",\n    \"source_url\": \"https://minimalistbaker.com/1-bowl-chocolate-chip-banana-bread-vegan-gf/\",\n    \"thumbnail_image_url\": \"https://minimalistbaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1-Bowl-Chocolate-Chip-Banana-Bread-Vegan-GF-STUNNING-moist-perfectly-sweet-rich-with-chocolate-minimalistbaker-9.jpg\",\n    \"ingredients\": [\n      \"3 medium ripe bananas (mashed)\",\n      \"1 tsp baking soda\",\n      \"1/2 tsp sea salt\",\n      \"1/3 cup melted coconut oil (or vegan butter)\",\n      \"1/2 cup organic cane sugar (or coconut sugar)\",\n      \"1/4 cup maple syrup\",\n      \"2 flax eggs (2 tbsp flaxseed meal + 5 tbsp water)\",\n      \"1 tsp vanilla extract\",\n      \"1 cup gluten-free oat flour\",\n      \"1 cup almond flour\",\n      \"1/2 cup potato starch (or arrowroot starch)\",\n      \"1/2 cup vegan chocolate chips (plus more for topping)\"\n    ],\n    \"cooking_instructions_summary\": \"Preheat your oven to 350°F (176°C) and line a loaf pan with parchment paper. In a large bowl, whisk the flax eggs and let them rest. Add the mashed bananas, baking soda, salt, melted coconut oil, sugar, maple syrup, and vanilla; whisk to combine. Add the oat flour, almond flour, and potato starch, stirring to combine. Gently fold in the chocolate chips. Pour into the prepared pan, top with extra chocolate chips, and bake for 60 to 70 minutes. Cool completely before slicing.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"recipe_title\": \"The Best Vegan Banana Bread (1-Bowl!)\",\n    \"source_url\": \"https://minimalistbaker.com/the-best-vegan-banana-bread/',\",\n    \"thumbnail_image_url\": \"https://minimalistbaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Vegan-Banana-Bread-1-Bowl-Simple-ingredients-SO-fluffy-perfectly-sweet-minimalistbaker-7.jpg\",\n    \"ingredients\": [\n      \"3 medium ripe bananas (mashed)\",\n      \"1/4 cup melted coconut oil (or vegan butter)\",\n      \"1/4 cup unsweetened applesauce\",\n      \"1/2 cup organic cane sugar\",\n      \"1/2 cup brown sugar\",\n      \"1 tsp vanilla extract\",\n      \"1 tsp baking soda\",\n      \"1/2 tsp sea salt\",\n      \"1 tsp ground cinnamon\",\n      \"1 1/2 cups unbleached all-purpose flour\",\n      \"1/2 cup rolled oats\"\n    ],\n    \"cooking_instructions_summary\": \"Preheat your oven to 350°F (176°C) and grease a loaf pan. Mash the bananas in a large bowl. Whisk in the melted oil, applesauce, cane sugar, brown sugar, vanilla, baking soda, salt, and cinnamon. Add the all-purpose flour and rolled oats, stirring gently until just combined. Transfer the batter into the prepared loaf pan and bake for 50 to 60 minutes until a toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean. Let cool before serving.\"\n  }\n]\n```","type":"text"}],"type":"model_output"}],"object":"interaction","model":"gemini-3.5-flash"}